whereas.text:
Whereas as of April 30, 2013, a total of 776,055 members
			 of the United States Armed Forces have deployed to Afghanistan and spent most
			 of their tour there;

Whereas in June 2011, President Barack Obama announced his
			 plan to begin the withdrawal of United States troops from Afghanistan, changing
			 the mission from one of combat to one of support;

Whereas the number of members of the United States Armed
			 Forces in Afghanistan, which peaked at about 100,000 in June 2011, was reduced
			 to a pre-surge level of about 66,000 as of September 20, 2012;

Whereas levels of members of the United States Armed
			 Forces are expected to fall to 34,000 by February 2014, with the bulk of that
			 drawdown to take place in the winter of 2013 to 2014;

Whereas the United States has depended upon the service
			 and sacrifices of generations of courageous citizens to protect and uphold the
			 Nation’s ideals;
